data.description: Slanting Bridge Rd. Welcome to this very well maintained charming 3-bed's, 2-bath ranch home, built in 2016! It's conveniently located and offers a comfortable living experience. The large flat completely fenced in rear yard and custom built deck is spectacular! The property is perfect for outdoor activities, entertaining and relaxing! The side load garage with extra driveway space; poured concrete & rocking chair front porch offers nice curb appeal. The inside offers many upgrades from flooring to granite countertops in kitchen and bath. A MUST SEE!!
